abalho especiais para “deliberar sobre uma política nacional de inteligência artificial, tanto no campo civil como de segurança”. Ele também falou sobre a necessidade de os governos compreenderem os perigos da inteligência artificial. Avaliou que Israel poderia ser um ator global significativo na questão."},{"subtype":"twitter","referent":{"referent_properties":{"additional_properties":{"comments":[],"_id":1708352809648}},"provider":"https://publish.twitter.com/oembed?url=","service":"oembed","id":"https://twitter.com/IsraeliPM/status/1665726107650334723","type":"twitter"},"_id":"MOMDRGPTTJHLLDPKLULWUDFJXU","raw_oembed":{"author_name":"Prime Minister of Israel","cache_age":"3153600000","provider_url":"https://twitter.com","type":"twitter","version":"1.0","url":"https://twitter.com/IsraeliPM/status/1665726107650334723","author_url":"https://twitter.com/IsraeliPM","width":550,"html":"<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">PM Netanyahu:<br><br>We are at the dawn of a new era for humanity, an era of artificial intelligence. <br><br>Last night I had a long conversation with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/elonmusk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@elonmusk</a>, whose insight and contribution to humanity I hold in high esteem. <a href=\"https://t.co/ZyyvvntjKC\">pic.twitter.com/ZyyvvntjKC</a></p>&mdash; Prime Minister of Israel (@IsraeliPM) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IsraeliPM/status/1665726107650334723?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 5, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n\n","_id":"https://twitter.com/IsraeliPM/status/1665726107650334723","additional_properties":{"comments":[],"_id":1708352809648},"provider_name":"Twitter","height":null},"type":"oembed_response"},{"level":3,"_id":"7YIZS4VO4RFWBKO72OY3FTSXSM","additional_properties":{"inline_comments":[],"comments":[],"_id":1708352809649},"type":"header","content":"Encontro entre Musk e Netanyahu"},{"_id":"DGAHVEZDABC75DJEDZVJ3XCASM","